    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold mb-6">Policy Wonk</h1>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto opacity-90">
      Check your public policy knowledge in a fun way. Most fun if you're a Takshashila alumnus or a public policy enthusiast.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-10 text-sm opacity-70">
      Iqbal Ji is still tying his neck collar. Please hold.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
